So anyway, there is some spray out there that you can use on items that cannot be washed, but it's been a long time so I don't remember what the name was. And also, things like comforters and pillows can be thrown in the dryer for a cycle at the hottest setting to kill them as well... That's what my mom had my sister do with her pillows and comforters.<br>
